{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cosmic Waves is an entirely new take on the classic arcade genre of block destruction. It merges the well known gameplay elements like different block types and pickups with many new and cool features like: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Force wave emitting towers</strong> - control the ball's direction with the towers, enhancing its power. Burst through blocks and activate unique reactions of the objects on the level.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/Towers.gif?t=1739437793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bosses and Enemies</strong> - it's not only about destroying blocks, there are boss fights and other machines only waiting to be smashed to pieces! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/sphere.gif?t=1739437793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cool Characters and story\u00a0</strong>-  you can choose your main character each with their own special attack and also meet others on your way to save the galaxy from the evil empire! It's a simple, light-hearted plot with great and funny dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/Enemies_n.png?t=1739437793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Upgrade System</strong> - gather resources and upgrade everything! From the power of your special weapons, paddle's durability to tower's range you can create many different upgrade loadouts and aim for a high score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/upgrade.gif?t=1739437793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bonus levels</strong> - bonus levels to get more of those points and resources!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Destruction</strong> - what's better than simply destroying blocks? Blocks that crumble into pieces while you hit or shoot at them! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Time manipulation</strong> - slow down the time to aim the towers or move out of harm's way. It helps with precision aiming and some crazy combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Varied level objects</strong> - there are not only many block types but also many other objects with fun and unique effects for you to discover . Maybe you could also try hitting them with those towers? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Incredible Music</strong> - and on top of it all a great soundtrack made by Module!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739437793","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739437793","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739437793","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739437793","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cosmic Waves is an entirely new take on the classic arcade genre of block destruction. It merges the well known gameplay elements like different block types and pickups with many new and cool features like: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\